{"tid":1354992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[大快人心 有圖]何家山墳何家猜","createTime":"2019-07-23T08:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T01:27:32.000Z","uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1660d6c6867c8b61498895d501c6c74bf65476","tid":1354992,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:47:12.000Z","msg":"sorry又呃左大家入嚟<br />\n相信大家呢個moment都爽緊 打緊飛機<br />\n我自己都覺得咁唔小心滑倒了真無陰公<br />\n<br />\n但係同時都要麻煩各位手足諗下後果會係點<br />\n我地既活動搞得咁順(唔係政府回應順) 好大程度係政府引起既民怨已經令市民開始覺得抗爭係出路<br />\n但係今次搞著'先人' '父母' 呢啲咁敏感既角色<br />\n身為有道德既香港人一定會有感受<br />\n好似我地之前一路煲緊既專講老弱 大肚婆咁<br />\n對家/我地自己都一定會對今次拆墳有好大回響<br />\n所以我地絕對需要度度 到底點做<br />\n<br />\n民意唔係最重要 但係絕對需要concern <br />\n佢唔係一個推動力 但係絕對會係一個阻力<br />\n明既就明 唔洗屌我p牌仔 我只係講事實"},{"pid":"bd6aa36cf7a932fb2fb92ac6393c004f56d270bb","tid":1354992,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:48:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>集中一個post講得唔得?</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"137e6e16069e1ec840c6acb604493514e1492f7c","tid":1354992,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd6aa36cf7a932fb2fb92ac6393c004f56d270bb","tid":1354992,"uid":23373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:48:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>集中一個post講得唔得?</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:49:09.000Z","msg":"啲po快撚過火箭點講?"},{"pid":"bc7c5bc114c76de93f1bde1fd2a6adbf1d649637","tid":1354992,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:51:02.000Z","msg":"推佢老母"},{"pid":"e5e2da08d3957dd5f7e52dd5bf04f19c5d171a16","tid":1354992,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:53:30.000Z","msg":"我再推 今次要拆彈"},{"pid":"2d51fe4a0e43a7d49d3234bacac91df0ad39e6d2","tid":1354992,"uid":285367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T08:56:31.00